Damas RNP Web Service interface by an RNP user who wishes to Nominate. 
Web services are built on industry standard technologies. 
They are available on the Internet and ensure the same level of the privacy and security as RNP Damas web site.


Interface of Damas Web Services

Production:	https://rnp.unicorn.com/DamasService2.svc		https	443

